currentDoc: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

currentSuggestions.original: Apparently, it was the first time I had been born and it did not go quite as planned.
currentSuggestions.trimmed: Apparently, it was the first time I had been born and it did not go quite as planned.

currentSuggestions.original: My head is so small it looks like a piece of cauliflower.

currentSuggestions.trimmed: I am a girl, and you are not the father.
